---
layout: layouts/component-demo.njk
title: Label
description: a label associated with a form input
nhsuk: https://service-manual.nhs.uk/design-system/components/label
---

{% from "components/label/macro.njk" import label %}
{% from "components/hint/macro.njk" import hint %}

<h2>Default</h2>
<div>
  {{ label({ for: "fullname", text: "Full name" }) }}
  <input id="fullname" type="text" class="form">
</div>

<h2>As page heading</h2>
<p>When the label is the page's primary question, set
  <code>isPageHeading: true</code> so it is also rendered as an
  <code>&lt;h1&gt;</code>.</p>

<div>
  {{ label({
    for: "nhs-number",
    text: "What is your NHS number?",
    isPageHeading: true
  }) }}
  {{ hint({
    id: "nhs-number-hint",
    text: "It is a 10-digit number."
  }) }}
  <input id="nhs-number"
         type="text"
         aria-describedby="nhs-number-hint"
         class="form">
</div>
